Package: libpocsag0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: POCSAG paging protocol encoder/decoder library
 libpocsag is a C library for encoding and decoding POCSAG (Post Office
 Code Standardisation Advisory Group) paging protocol messages. It provides
 a batch encoder, streaming decoder, BCH(31,21) error correction, FSK
 modulator/demodulator, baseband NRZ output, and support for numeric,
 alphanumeric, and tone-only message types.

Package: libpocsag-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libpocsag0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: POCSAG paging protocol encoder/decoder library (development files)
 libpocsag is a C library for encoding and decoding POCSAG (Post Office
 Code Standardisation Advisory Group) paging protocol messages.
 .
 This package contains the header files and pkg-config file needed
 to build programs that use libpocsag.
